openconsensus.trace

Class AttributeValue

  • java.lang.Object
    • openconsensus.trace.AttributeValue

  • @Immutable
public abstract class AttributeValue
extends Object
    A class that represents all the possible values for an attribute. An attribute can have 4 types of values: String, boolean, long or double, represented through AttributeValue.Type.
    Since:
    0.1.0

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes

      static class  AttributeValue.Type
      An enum that represents all the possible value types for an AttributeValue.
